libnfcdef
=========

Library for parsing and building NFC Data Exchange Format (NDEF)
messages.

The NFC Data Exchange Format (NDEF) is a common data format used for
exchanging data between NFC devices and NFC tags, or between two NFC
devices.

libnfcdef supports Media-Type records and a few common well known types:
Text ("T"), URI ("U") and SmartPoster ("Sp") 
